                     <interp inst="t18280410-231-person1299" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer, and took him in charge; I found a picture and an Italian iron on him.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written defence, pleading intoxication.</p>

